---
title: Mexican Steak Tortas with Charred Poblanos
description: Tortas bring all the flavours of your favourite tacos to a nice and toasty roll. Toppings like chipotle-spiced steak, poblano pepper, and a blend of Mexican cheeses make it a winner in the flavour department.  Grab a napkin and get ready to dig in!
